      <title>自峰会以来，Big Tech以1.6万亿美元的赔偿进入更正</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/magnificent-7-dips-into-correction-territory-with-tesla-lagging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两年内，美国股票增长了54％的七种技术庞然大物已经跌入了集体纠正，突出了美国股票的烦恼时刻，因为担心经济正在放缓，通货膨胀将会加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/magnificent-7-dips-into-correction-territory-with-tesla-lagging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 14:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice France，债权人附近的债权人来重组债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/altice-france-creditors-are-near-a-deal-to-restructure-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁帕特里克·德拉希（Patrick Drahi）的电信提供商Altice France接近与债权人达成协议，以将公司的债务堆积86亿欧元（90亿美元）削减，以换取非控制权股权和治理股权和治理变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/altice-france-creditors-are-near-a-deal-to-restructure-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 14:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西海上石油被监管机构击打钻探击中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/brazil-offshore-oil-hit-by-regulator-s-crackdown-on-drilling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西监管机构正在镇压石油巨头和Equinor ASA等石油巨头的一些海上钻探，这使勘探和生产项目变得复杂，这是该国努力提高原油产量的关键时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/brazil-offshore-oil-hit-by-regulator-s-crackdown-on-drilling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 09:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
